=============================================================================
USAGE EXAMPLES
=============================================================================

{{ free_indirect_thought("Clarissa",
    "looked at the flowers in the shop window",
    "What a pity they would fade",
    "She remembered once bringing flowers to Bourton — roses, white roses",
    "But that was years ago; she was different then, or was she?") }}
Output: "Clarissa looked at the flowers in the shop window. What a pity they would fade. She remembered once bringing flowers to Bourton — roses, white roses. But that was years ago; she was different then, or was she?"

{{ moment_of_being("She",
    "was sewing the dress, her needle going in and out, in and out",
    "the whole room seemed to fill with light — the light of a summer afternoon thirty years ago",
